1. Create a Resouce

POST -> http://localhost:8080/tasks

{
    "description" : "singing"
}

2. Retrieve  all resources

GET -> http://localhost:8080/tasks

3. To retrieve task by id

GET -> http://localhost:8080/tasks/1

4. Update the resource

PUT -> http://localhost:8080/tasks/1

{
    "id": 1,
    "description": "flute"
}


5. To get API documentation

OPTIONS -> http://localhost:8080/tasks

and

OPTIONS -> http://localhost:8080/tasks/<task-id>
